items.title: Bradley robs Davis of HR with leaping grab
items.summary: Jackie Bradley Jr. has home run robbery down to a science. The Red Sox's standout center fielder raced back to the wall, timed his leap perfectly and took a solo shot away from Orioles slugger Chris Davis on the first pitch of the bottom of the fifth inning on Tuesday night at Camden Yards.
